This paper discusses a method for improving the accuracy and efficiency of non-iterative co-simulations by reducing coupling errors and ensuring energy conservation. The paper involves concepts related to modeling and simulation (MS), control systems (SY), numerical analysis (NA), civil engineering (CE), and robotics (RO). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.MS and cs.SY, followed by cs.NA, cs.CE, and cs.RO.
